    "privacy-map-desc": "For displaying maps.",
    "privacy-ai-title": "AI Algorithms:",
    "privacy-ai-desc": "We use neural networks and intelligent algorithms to create personalized recommendations (e.g., clothing advice). Your weather queries are processed anonymously and are not used to train third-party AI models.",
