    "privacy-sec4-desc": "We do not use tracking cookies. We only use technically necessary mechanisms to save your preferences.",
    "privacy-sec5-title": "5. Data Export and Processing",
    "privacy-sec5-desc": "The data export functionality (JSON, CSV, Excel) works entirely on your browser's side. No generated reports are sent to our servers; they are only stored on your device.",
